---
title: "Superfunk Roller Disco: The UK's largest and funkiest Mobile Roller Disco operator"
meta:
  description: 'Superfunk Roller Disco are proud to lead the revival of a cult fun activity from the 70s and 80s and are taking it around the UK.'
---
{%- from "component.njk" import component with context -%}
{%- extends "layouts/default.njk" -%}

{%- set sectionClasses = "px-4 py-8 space-y-8 lg:py-10" -%}
{%- set sectionHeaderClasses = "container max-w-xl mx-auto space-y-2 text-center" -%}
{%- set sectionPreHeadlineClasses = "-mb-2 text-base font-medium tracking-wide text-pink-600 uppercase lg:text-lg" -%}
{%- set sectionHeadlineClasses = "font-semibold text-3xl text-slate-100 tracking-wide lg:text-4xl" -%}
{%- set sectionLeadClasses = "text-xl font-medium text-slate-100 lg:text-2xl" -%}
{%- set bodyText = "text-center text-xl font-normal text-slate-100 md:text-left lg:text-2xl !leading-[1.35]" -%}
{# TODO: leading sizing #}

{% block header %}
  {{ component('header') }}
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
<main>

  {#- START: Intro -#}
  <div class="{{ sectionClasses }}">
    <header class="{{ sectionHeaderClasses }}">
      <p class="{{ sectionPreHeadlineClasses }}">Superfunk</p>
      <h1 class="{{ sectionHeadlineClasses }}">Roller Disco Hire</h1>
      <p class="{{ sectionLeadClasses }}">Superfunk Roller Disco is proud to lead the revival of a cult fun activity from the 70s and 80s.</p>
    </header>
    <figure class="aspect-video container max-w-5xl bg-red-100">
      <picture>
        <img alt="" class="" height="720" src="/assets/images/home-01.jpg" width="1280">
      </picture>
    </figure>
    <div class="{{ bodyText }} container max-w-4xl space-y-6">
      <p>We have 14 yearsâ€™ experience in delivering roller disco events to schools, colleges, universities, leisure centres, festival organisers and corporate clients.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  {#- END: Intro -#}

  {#- START: Gallery -#}
  <div class="relative w-full flex gap-4 snap-x snap-mandatory overflow-x-auto pl-4">
    <div class="snap-center shrink-0 w-4/5 sm:w-auto">
      <img alt="" class="object-cover h-52 w-full rounded-lg sm:h-auto sm:w-96" height="322" src="/assets/images/home-quadrollerdiscoskates-2018.jpg" width="572">
    </div>
    <div class="snap-center shrink-0 w-4/5 sm:w-auto">
      <img alt="" class="object-cover h-52 w-full rounded-lg sm:h-auto sm:w-96" height="322" src="/assets/images/home-naturalhistorymuseum-rollerdisco-2022.jpg" width="572">
    </div>
    <div class="snap-center shrink-0 w-4/5 sm:w-auto">
      <img alt="" class="object-cover h-52 w-full rounded-lg sm:h-auto sm:w-96" height="322" src="/assets/images/home-carfestfestival-rollerdisco-2019.jpg" width="572">
    </div>
    <div class="snap-center shrink-0 w-4/5 sm:w-auto">
      <img alt="" class="object-cover h-52 w-full rounded-lg sm:h-auto sm:w-96" height="322" src="/assets/images/home-rollerdisco-universityofsheffield--2022.jpg" width="572">
    </div>
    <div class="snap-center shrink-0 w-4/5 sm:w-auto">
      <img alt="" class="object-cover h-52 w-full rounded-lg sm:h-auto sm:w-96" height="322" src="/assets/images/home-inlinerollerdiscoskates-2019.jpg" width="572">
    </div>
    <div class="snap-center shrink-0 w-4/5 sm:w-auto">
      <img alt="" class="object-cover h-52 w-full rounded-lg sm:h-auto sm:w-96" height="322" src="/assets/images/home-manchesteracademy-rollerdisco-2021.jpg" width="572">
    </div>
    <div class="snap-center shrink-0 w-4/5 sm:w-auto">
      <img alt="" class="object-cover h-52 w-full rounded-lg sm:h-auto sm:w-96" height="322" src="/assets/images/home-adobesummit-rollerdisco-london-excel-2018.jpg" width="572">
    </div>
    <div class="snap-center shrink-0 w-4/5 sm:w-auto">
      <img alt="" class="object-cover h-52 w-full rounded-lg sm:h-auto sm:w-96" height="322" src="/assets/images/home-rollerdisco-solihullbirmingham-2021.jpg" width="572">
    </div>
  </div>
  {#- END: Gallery -#}

  {#- START: Services -#}
  <section class="{{ sectionClasses }}">
    <header class="{{ sectionHeaderClasses }}">
      <p class="{{ sectionPreHeadlineClasses }}">Experienced</p>
      <h2 class="{{ sectionHeadlineClasses }}">Mobile roller disco crew</h2>
      <p class="{{ sectionLeadClasses }}">We provide everything from standalone skate hire to full roller disco packages.</p>
    </header>
    {#- Background blur with images behind? #}
    <div class="container gap-6 grid grid-cols-1 items-stretch max-w-6xl mx-auto sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
      {%- for item in collections.services %}
        <article class="inline-flex flex-col rounded-2xl px-4 py-6 lg:p-8 border border-pink-600 bg-superfunk-dark">
          <header class="mb-4 flex flex-row-reverse items-center justify-between">
            {%- if item.data.service.heroicon_path1 %}
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 inline-flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-zinc-900">
              <svg aria-hidden="true" class="h-8 w-8" fill="none" height="32" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="32" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" >
                {{- item.data.service.heroicon_path | safe -}}
              </svg>
            </div>
            {% endif -%}
            <h3 class="font-semibold mr-auto pr-4 text-xl tracking-wide lg:text-2xl">
              {{- item.data.service.name -}}
              {#- <a href="{{ item.url }}">{{ item.data.service.name }}</a> -#}
            </h3>
          </header>
          {%- if item.data.service.excerpt %}
            <p class="text-lg text-opacity-80 text-white lg:text-xl">{{ item.data.service.excerpt }}</p>
          {% endif -%}
          {# <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="mt-auto h-8 w-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg> #}
        </article>
      {% endfor -%}
    </div>
    <div class="{{ bodyText }} container max-w-4xl space-y-6">
      <p>If your venue has a suitable flooring already then there is no need for a mobile rink or flooring cover. We can simply roll up with our skates and safety equipment.</p>
      <p>If you wish to set up your own regular roller disco, we can assist with this too providing advice, training for your staff, and equipment hire for a trial event before you commit to spending on equipment.</p>
      <p>Pricing is bespoke per event, so please <a class="text-pink-600 underline underline-offset-4 hover:no-underline hover:text-pink-500" href="/contact/">get in touch</a> with Rach for a quote.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  {#- END: Extra -#}

</main>
{% endblock %}

{% block footer %}
  {{ component('footer') }}
{% endblock %}
